On Thursday, June 14, 2007, at 09:19AM, "Anymouse" <honeybus(-at-)gmail.com> wrote:

>Is there s gasket between the oil pressure switch and the case??

If your switch has straight threads you need a copper gasket to help seal it. If it has tapered threads (like pipe thread) you don't.

